{"tid":956351,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【非洲豬瘟】74噸飼料驗出病毒 來自天津12間屠房","createTime":"2018-12-26T07:45:26.000Z","updateTime":"2018-12-26T07:54:13.000Z","uid":51620,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"785ee02397176647968f9b517e39e80005d19c2a","tid":956351,"uid":51620,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-26T07:45:26.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/china/realtime/article/20181226/59070936?fbclid=IwAR0mWrw7K-XlBwzrUFt1K8WDtH3Z55pGfgzX905qDQ62InnKwXED0cPazhU\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fchina%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20181226%2F59070936%3Ffbclid%3DIwAR0mWrw7K-XlBwzrUFt1K8WDtH3Z55pGfgzX905qDQ62InnKwXED0cPazhU&d=q9MF6Eci48e2Ovyajk6KCf7vEz4FU%2Bq4m%2F6ZFrWLoTs%3D&h=443c108d\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fchina%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20181226%2F59070936%3Ffbclid%3DIwAR0mWrw7K-XlBwzrUFt1K8WDtH3Z55pGfgzX905qDQ62InnKwXED0cPazhU&h=eeada485\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/china/realtime/article/20181226/59070936?fbclid=IwAR0mWrw7K-XlBwzrUFt1K8WDtH3Z55pGfgzX905qDQ62InnKwXED0cPazhU</a><br />\n<br />\n非洲豬瘟病毒在內地肆虐，中國海關總署今日公佈，上星期五在天津兩批準備出口的豬血漿蛋白粉，驗出非洲豬瘟病毒。有關原料來自天津12間屠房，共計73.93噸。<br />\n<br />\n中國海關總署日發佈警示通報稱，本月21日，天津海關在天津恩彼蛋白質有限公司所生產的兩批豬血漿蛋白粉，檢出非洲豬瘟病毒核酸陽性反應，這些產品共計73.93噸，原料來自天津地區12個屠宰加工廠。<br />\n<br />\n當局要求全面對出口加工企業的豬源性成份飼料，加強非洲豬瘟病毒檢測，當結果呈陽性時，就要立即封存有關產品，並追蹤源頭。<br />\n<br />\n總署又要求特別是供港澳飼養場，確保豬源性飼料的安全，對使用的豬血漿蛋白粉，展開非洲豬瘟病毒檢測，若發現有問題，要立即停用及向部門報告。"},{"pid":"056e4df0b3c2d858dbc3d418dccedad8c2c7111f","tid":956351,"uid":51620,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-26T07:53:28.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f3cf9e1aac81cafce4c6a7dc9b8c5fbbe6bff51a","tid":956351,"uid":72009,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-26T07:54:13.000Z","msg":"正，快速傳染全國"}]}